I"8<h1 id="challenge-3---print-a-right-angled-triangle">Challenge 3 - Print a Right-Angled Triangle</h1>

<h1 id="problem-statement">Problem Statement</h1>
<ul>
  <li>Write a code which prints a right-angled triangle of the character <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&amp;</code>.</li>
</ul>

<p>The code takes an integer variable row as input and prints the right-angled triangle with that number of rows displaying <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&amp;</code>.</p>

<p>The base of the right-angled triangle is the input number, i.e., input of n will yield a triangle of base n</p>

<p>Input</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> positive integer
 
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>Output</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> right-angled triangle
 
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>Sample Input</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>   5
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Sample Output</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>   &amp;
   &amp;&amp;
   &amp;&amp;&amp;
   &amp;&amp;&amp;&amp;
   &amp;&amp;&amp;&amp;&amp;
   
</code></pre></div></div>

